casebody.data:
Patrick L. JUNE and Molly M. June, Plaintiffs-Appellants,
v.
Jeffrey Douglas TUTTLE and Stephanie Tuttle, Defendants,
and
Quality Converters, Inc. and Quality Camping, Inc., Defendants-Appellees. SC: 157998
COA: 339597 Supreme Court of Michigan. December 4, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the May 15, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
